<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Chicken Note</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="edn242">  242  HCE is posing a distorted version of Shem's &lsquo;first riddle of the universe&rsquo; from I.7: <i>When is a man not a man?</i> Shem's answer (which only he himself knew) is: <i>When he is a sham!</i>  </div>
